name: JTS
description: JTS Savior is a new generation of Defi decentralized financial application developed in conjunction with Binance Chain. JTS will restart in November 2023 and continue to build basic consensus through the DAO organization, which lasted a total of 14 months. In this process, JTS has gathered a large number of enthusiasts who believe in decentralized finance, and jointly promoted JTS's overall influence on Defi.
